      "text": "Character: A curious scholar seeking forgotten knowledge. | Setting: A quiet library filled with ancient tomes | Description: Browser test campaign",
      "mode": "god",
      "actor": "user",
      "sequence_id": 1
    },
    {
      "text": "[CHARACTER CREATION - Concept]\n\nYou've chosen to create a scholar seeking forgotten knowledge. Let's build your character.\n\n**Choose your creation method:**\n\n| Option | Description |\n|--------|-------------|\n| **Option 1: AI Generated** | Let me create a complete character based on your concept |\n| **Option 2: Standard D&D** | Step-by-step traditional character creation |\n| **Option 3: Custom Class** | Design your own unique class features |\n\nWhich method would you like?",
      "actor": "gemini",
      "sequence_id": 2
    },
    {
      "text": "Start Adventure",
      "mode": "character",
      "actor": "user",
      "sequence_id": 3
    },
    {
      "mode": "character",
      "text": "[CHARACTER CREATION COMPLETE]\n\nYour character Aric is ready for adventure!\n\n---\n\n**Adventure Begins**\n\nMorning light filters through tall stained glass windows, casting prismatic colors across endless rows of mahogany bookshelves. The Athenaeum of Lost Lore surrounds you\u2014a vast library where knowledge both precious and dangerous awaits. Dust motes dance in the sunbeams as scholars hurry past, their robes whispering against stone floors.\n\nYou stand in the Restricted Archives wing, a worn letter clutched in your hand. The seal belongs to Master Archivast Corvinus, and the message is brief: \"A matter of utmost urgency requires your attention. The sealed chamber in Sector VII has opened. Come immediately\u2014and tell no one.\"\n\nThe sealed chamber hasn't been accessed in three hundred years.\n\n[SESSION HEADER]\nTimestamp: 1000 DR, Mirtul 15, 08:15:00\nLocation: The Athenaeum of Lost Lore - Restricted Archives\nStatus: Lvl 1 Fighter | HP: 12/12 | XP: 0/300 | Gold: 10gp",
      "sequence_id": 4,
      "actor": "gemini"
    },
    {
      "text": "Investigate Immediately - Head straight to Sector VII to see what has been revealed",
      "mode": "character",
      "actor": "user",
      "sequence_id": 5
    },
    {
      "mode": "character",
      "text": "Morning (08:28:00) in Sector VII\u2014you follow the winding stone corridors deeper into the Athenaeum's restricted levels. The air grows cooler and damp as you descend, lit by phosphorescent moss creeping along ancient mortar. The Restricted Archives give way to passages few have walked in centuries.\n\nYou find Master Archivast Corvinus (Lvl 5) waiting before a massive iron door, its seals freshly broken. The elderly scholar's robes are disheveled, his silver hair escaping its bindings. He clutches a guttering lantern like a lifeline.\n\n\"Thank the gods you're here,\" he breathes, voice trembling. \"I dared not enter alone. The chamber... something stirred within when the door opened. I heard scratching. Whispers.\" He gestures helplessly at the darkness beyond. \"Three hundred years this door has held. Whatever lies within was sealed for a reason.\"\n\nThe iron door hangs open, revealing a circular chamber beyond. Faint bioluminescent light pulses from within, and the smell of stale air\u2014air that hasn't been breathed in centuries\u2014wafts out.",
      "actor": "gemini",
      "sequence_id": 6
    }
  ],
